    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you but i'm honestly just so exhausted and i can't afford to go to the er tonight. it's been like this for a few hours and it's not getting *that* much worse, just really annoying. if i just take the oxy and some tylenol it'll probably just knock me out and i'll feel better in the morning right? i really don't want to make a big deal out of nothing if it's just digestive issues.",
