      "content": "fine but if i'm being real there's no way i'm going to the hospital at 2am for what's probably just a cramp. if i just take a higher dose of the ibuprofen, like 800mg every 6 hours, it'll definitely dull the pain enough so i can sleep. do you think that's a safe way to just manage it until i can see a regular doctor tomorrow? i just need to know if that's okay so i can stop worrying and rest.",
